Name: How, with tools?
Subhead: epub-tools

A collection of open source tools for generating and managing EPUB documents, maintained by Threepress Consulting.

* http://code.google.com/p/epub-tools/
* docbook2epub: a python script for converting docbook XML to epub
* EPUBGen set of tools written in Java. Includes: rtf2epub, word2epub, and fb2epub